Allah has created women weak
So, Allah has ordered only few ahkam(four):

1) Prayers 
2) Fasting in Ramadan
3) Iffat & Paak daaman
4) Pharma bardaar to husband


So, 
> Please sleep in time and wake up for prayers, in time.
> Please understand the intricacies of prayers amidst cycles


